<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3157906" xml-lang="en-US"><ahelp hid=".uno:ZoomPlus">Displays the slide at two times its current size.</ahelp></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3145822" xml-lang="en-US">You can also select the <emph>Zoom In </emph>tool and drag a rectangular frame around the area you want to enlarge.</paragraph>
